	[em 
		"KOF '96
	]em
	") is a fighting game released by SNK for the Neo Geo arcade and home consoles in 1996. It is the third game of the series, following 
	[em 
		"The King of Fighters '95
	]em
	". Like its predecessor, the game was ported to the Neo-Geo CD, as well as the PlayStation and Sega Saturn. The game made a few changes to gameplay such as new techniques, various changes of some teams, with a few of them introducing new characters.
